        <item>
            <title>Version 1.0.2</title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                    <h2>Version 1.0.2 - Global Hotkeys</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Global Keyboard Shortcuts:</strong> Control Pace from any app</li>
                        <li>⌃⌥O - Cycle through focus modes (Rectangle → Square → Center Column → Circle)</li>
                        <li>⌃⌥P - Cycle through sizes (S → M → L)</li>
                        <li>⌃⌥L - Turn overlay off</li>
                        <li>⌃⌥F - Toggle focus message window</li>
                        <li>Shortcuts displayed in menu bar and side panel</li>
                        <li>ESC key now properly closes focus message window</li>
                        <li>Requires Input Monitoring permission (one-time setup)</li>
                    </ul>
                ]]>
            </description>
